Prema normi HRN EN 61082-1 postoje četiri osnovne vrste dokumenata za elektrotehniku:
- dijagrami (strujne sheme, blok sheme, nacrti koji nisu u mjerilu)
- nacrti (pregledni nacrti, dispozicije opreme, mjerne skice, nacrti u mjerilima)
- tablice (liste)
- grafovi (time sequence chartž

podvrste dijagrama:
 - overview diagram
   - singe-line diagram
   - network map
   - **topological diagram of a network** (IEC 60050-603)
   - system diagram
   - system operational diagram
   - three phase system diagram
   - voltage map
   - block diagram   
 - function diagram
   - function chart
   - equivalent-circuit diagram
   - logic-function diagram   
 - circuit diagram
   - terminal funcion diagram
 - connection diagram 
   - terminal connection diagram
   - unit connection diagram
   - interconnection diagram
   - cable diagram
   - terminal connection table
   - unit connection list
   - unit connection table
   - interconnection list
   - interconnection table
   - cable list
   - cable table

 podvrste nacrta
 - arrangement drawing
   - site plan
   - earthing diagram
   - installation diagram
   - cable routing diagram
   - earthing plan
   - installation drawing
   - building drawing
   - assembly drawing
   

podvrste tablica
- connection diagram

podvrste grafova
 - time sequence chart
 - sequence chart
